summary:
DARK PEPE - $DEPE

Laser Eyes Pepe Coin is a memecoin that ​blends the virality of internet memes
​with the excitement of ​cryptocurrency. Inspired by the ​popular "Pepe the
Frog" meme and the ​"laser eyes" trend among crypto ​enthusiasts, this coin
aims to bring ​fun and community spirit to the world ​of digital assets.
